data.description: This is such a lovely and inviting home - a pleasure to present and show! It is bright and comfortable, cheery and peaceful. 3 bedrooms / 2 bathrooms are included in the split floorplan. The Master bedroom has a walk-in closet, a large bathroom with both a shower and big soaker tub; and a skylight adds both lighting and depth to the room. There are also double sinks and extra cabinet space, too. Kitchen and dining areas are convenient and complimentary, with an easy flow into the living room. The dining area provides additional cabinet space appealingly built-in to the wall, and there is a pantry closet in the kitchen, as well. The Sellers have taken such good care of the property and it certainly shows, inside and outside. Landscaping in the front is diverse and colorful, established and well-groomed with the added convenience of an inground sprinkler system. A detached 1-car garage is included plus there is double parking in front of it on concrete, as well as additional parking at the curb. The back yard is fenced and the storage building conveys with the property.
